iles.wordpress.org/ohiowebpro\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d5801f2388436045c0e0316ec357d53?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8d5801f2388436045c0e0316ec357d53?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ohiowebpro\" class=\"reviewer-name\">ohiowebpro</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 5, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I have the pro version of this software and support seems to not care. In calendar view, after you switch months, you cannot click the view all link within a day. Notified support months ago, and they admitted it was an issue with the plugin and that it would be fixed in the next version. Only that never happened. Still broken months later. They have been no help for a temporary solution. They are only focused on rolling out the next version of features, and not fixing bugs. I would stay away from anything by Modern Tribe.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good plugin with correct server settings...</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/screenload\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc70ad2781cf47fc61c296d3cfbc5d05?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/bc70ad2781cf47fc61c296d3cfbc5d05?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/screenload\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Screenload <small>(screenload)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 10, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">This plugin causes me nothing but trouble.\n\n<del datetime=\"2019-12-10T12:55:38+00:00\">Errors, wrong URLs,</del> shortcodes not working like intended...\n\n<del datetime=\"2019-12-10T12:55:38+00:00\">And today we had some angry guests because the TIME is displayed one hour off.</del>\n\n<del datetime=\"2019-12-10T12:55:38+00:00\">10 am inside WordPress backend, 9 am displayed on the front end. I mean.. wtf?</del></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">..simply Great</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cirowordpress\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7f860170ca6740d7f99fe767c924c89e?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/7f860170ca6740d7f99fe767c924c89e?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/cirowordpress\" class=\"reviewer-name\">cirowp <small>(cirowordpress)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Well done...clean ...easy to use anche powerfull at the same time. Great plugin, in my opinion the best events calendar!</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Bullet Proof</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mongrel\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c3e13f9d247a89f9e310d7235b6b0ae?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/8c3e13f9d247a89f9e310d7235b6b0ae?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mongrel\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mongrel</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 30, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">What can I say? It\'s the one that works. Every time.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Terrible soporte en su versión de Ticket Plus</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joelramirezleal\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dce08a2c7b602e51b0c73ddd48410556?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/dce08a2c7b602e51b0c73ddd48410556?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/joelramirezleal\" class=\"reviewer-name\">joelramirezleal</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">November 21, 2019</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">No lo recomendaría si no existe alguna otra alternativa, el soporte hasta el momento es terrible. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Works great!</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/terryflhamilton\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/44d729f4e5fe4d1cd0d3b15f62160a47?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=